🚀 Introducing HireReadyAI

Currently I am working in an Lab4Tech which provides technical training for those who is seeking for job opportunities. Profilers and Job seekers really don't know of exactly how well their profile fits a role, which skills are missing, how to prepare for interviews in a focused way.

So to help both the profile and job seeker  I built HireRaedyAI combining CV analysis, job-description skill extraction, skill-gap matching, personalized interview preparation, adaptive practice, and RAG-grounded learning material.
