- support SQL code execution in a safe sandbox
- add stronger adaptive learning profiles across multiple sessions
- add user-level saved learning paths and longitudinal progress
- add production deployment hardening, monitoring, and audit logs
- add bias and fairness checks for scoring and feedback
- add OpenAI provider support alongside Mistral for configurable LLM usage

This project gave me a much clearer understanding of what production-style LLM systems need: structured data contracts, retrieval strategy, evaluation, observability, and user-centered workflows.

